{"to":["info@rainbowfertility.com"],"subject":"Initial Consultation Request – Jane & Alex","body":"Hello Rainbow Fertility Care Team,

My partner Alex and I are excited to begin our family-building journey and would like to schedule an initial consultation with your clinic.

To help you prepare, here is some preliminary information:

• Intended parents: Jane (31) and Alex (32), a same-sex female couple.
• Reason for visit: Discussion of fertility treatment options (IUI vs. IVF) and selection of donor sperm.
• Medical note: Alex has a family history of fraternal twins. Our personal physician, Dr. Emily Harris, advised pursuing a personalized treatment plan.
• Preferred dates: Weekdays between 15–20 March or 5–10 April. We are flexible on appointment times.
• Questions we hope to cover:
   – Success rates for IUI and IVF with lesbian couples
   – Legal considerations for family-building in our state
   – Lifestyle or dietary recommendations before treatment

Please let us know the next steps, any paperwork or medical records you would like us to forward beforehand, and available appointment slots that align with the windows above.

Thank you for supporting LGBT families. We look forward to working with your team.

Warm regards,
Jane & Alex","cc":null,"bcc":null,"execution_log_path":"data/logs/item46_execution_log.json"}
